enhanced_by.reason: The account method provides the current state of the margin account, which is necessary to understand the context before estimating the next hourly interest rate.
The interestHistory method provides historical interest data, which can be used to calculate trends and predict the next hourly interest rate.
The interestRateHistory method provides historical interest rate data, which can be used to verify and compare with the next hourly interest rate estimation.
The crossMarginData method provides cross margin fee data, which can be used to verify the context and accuracy of the next hourly interest rate estimation.
